item.description:
Starting from PoliGraf 0.99b you can monitor the top N VM quickstats***** (1 to 20 VM per graph). Now you can find the bad *sses of your datacenters!

Of course you can also search and pick some VM of your choice to compare their stats. The legend is formated as such to help you locate any tango: &lt;cluster_name&gt;.&lt;vm_name&gt;

In the PoliGraf 0.99d release, we revisited this dashboard to add snapshot usage (storage.
